{"title":"诗二首","authors":["马凯"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":2,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都江堰感怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每临都江堰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心涛总难平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏此壮举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类古文明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先人独慧眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神斧巧天成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼嘴分泯江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯盛皆由人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌口引来水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进排自掌门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郎侍溢洪道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙水各有循。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作堰正好低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘滩恰到深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇弯则截角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逢正即抽心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沃野千顷地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惠泽万代民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功德同日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治水训古今。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰亭探游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流觞曲水竞高歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉笔兰亭冠墨河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑舞云游随惬意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉奔龙走任欢波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势斜反正山旁树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲断还连池上鹅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但把永和神韵借，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新毫也敢试婆娑。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}